quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,40,""
  15,41,"(Allâh) said: "
  15,42,""
  16,19,"And Allâh knows what you conceal and what you reveal."
  16,20,"Those whom they (Al-Mushrikûn{1}) invoke besides Allâh have not created anything, but are themselves created.",footnotes:1:(V.20) Al-Mushrikûn: i.e. polytheists, pagans, idolaters, disbelievers in the Oneness of Allâh, those who worship others along with Allâh, and also those who set up rivals with (or partners to) Allâh.
  16,21,"(They are) dead, not alive; and they know not when they will be raised up."